{"tid":672490,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"談陳奕迅的「聲音與唱法史」","createTime":"2018-05-21T05:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T14:25:13.000Z","uid":69850,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a7855a93d0e4fdfbf3b119d705b9ba5d5e9d98","tid":672490,"uid":69850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>1. 1996-1999 聲底雄厚，唱法青澀</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n啱啱出道嘅Eason把聲係十分雄厚、清晰，音域極廣，但唱功較遜，唱法有點模仿當紅歌王。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uWxIAW5gwd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuWxIAW5gwd4&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=88a7f912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uWxIAW5gwd4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CO9Im35Yzzo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCO9Im35Yzzo&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=951388b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CO9Im35Yzzo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jl_3hEWp9vI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Djl_3hEWp9vI&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8dc9e191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jl_3hEWp9vI</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2. 2000-2003 柔情滿瀉，開創新風格</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間Eason所投放嘅感情係最動人，唱法開始減少無謂嘅腔調，變得簡約輕鬆，容易入耳，聲音較真摰。呢種唱法亦影響2000後男歌手嘅風格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8NJVNkzhJM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8NJVNkzhJM4&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8f786f87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8NJVNkzhJM4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAotCGoKhD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgAotCGoKhD0&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cb50bc36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAotCGoKhD0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 2005-2009 聲音的巔峰，風格多元化</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果張敬軒、李克勤係高音質無損，咁呢段時間嘅Eason就係Hi-Res再加靚Bass。聲音辨識度極高，真假音轉換流暢，風格更係數一數二最多元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QHUNwcYPOWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQHUNwcYPOWM&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6fdebdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QHUNwcYPOWM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VON6EEdRB34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVON6EEdRB34&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=96ab9076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VON6EEdRB34</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yu1p5l3m5es\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYu1p5l3m5es&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6e530f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yu1p5l3m5es</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4. 2010-2014 聲底變沉、沙啞，但唱功更強、題材更貼社會</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nEason聲音改變嘅時間點就係2010，2010後嘅佢音域收窄，高音略不穩。係呢到我整理咗幾個聲底變差嘅原因:<br />\n<br />\n1. 原本戒左煙嘅佢係2009年尾開始食返，我估計係因為準備開始走Tour壓力變大，無線與四大關係破裂令最紅嘅Eason無緣勁歌金曲，要靠食煙減壓。<br />\n2. 《心的距離》一曲以及上五樓的快活整張國語碟過份Chur盡Eason把聲，聲底加速變老。<br />\n3. 2010年頭去北京宣傳時巧遇沙塵暴，令聲底受創。<br />\n4. DUO 18場遇上感冒，身心十分疲累，係令到聲音冇得返轉頭嘅關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，Eason仍然以強勁唱功搭救，歌曲內容更多探討人生與社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=URUIcYDq3_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DURUIcYDq3_I&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=647899ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=URUIcYDq3_I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-yKnlZlQ5ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-yKnlZlQ5ug&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7cbf72a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-yKnlZlQ5ug</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYw4uH80gcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoYw4uH80gcw&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b1ece370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYw4uH80gcw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LfGj3epxFd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLfGj3epxFd8&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8763743a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LfGj3epxFd8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5. 2015至今 聲底回穩，產量大減</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nEason漸漸退出頒獎禮，聲音不再沙啞，但去唔返當年嘅水平，唱功依然係數一數二最強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GSG7ziTzqOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGSG7ziTzqOU&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=060113bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GSG7ziTzqOU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bWdawOZ0mDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbWdawOZ0mDI&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8fe1e692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bWdawOZ0mDI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mr8NaPtPPRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMr8NaPtPPRk&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7f3c28de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mr8NaPtPPRk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽聞今年Eason會出返廣東碟(L.O.V.E.)，敬請期待</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EasonChanOfficial/videos/1986566308020239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEasonChanOfficial%2Fvideos%2F1986566308020239%2F&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e644e03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EasonChanOfficial/videos/1986566308020239/</a>"},{"pid":"4a15b0fb4b031807007df381fbe0d71207005044","tid":672490,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"新碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea5f394a000a2fe178b701eb39a0d3b96bcb5ee","tid":672490,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"最鐘意都係2."},{"pid":"545b8a0d240ac3e58ca50f11d86214a14c6228a3","tid":672490,"uid":157468,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"樓主個post淨係講左沙唔沙聲，之後post 一大段youtube link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唱法淨係用唱功好黎形容，咁唱功好姐係包括咩，唔怪得張學友話D人唔明歌手唱緊d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88aa63aef6fe6fdeb8febfcfae0050bde29ec485","tid":672490,"uid":187617,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"聽完&ldquo;我們&rsquo; 覺得而家嘅eason唱功又升左lev咁，新碟應該今年出啦，有廣東國語，好似有啲似以前張H3M加stranger under my skin咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7092141d55ffa8ebbd9df4638289a61fb31fa126","tid":672490,"uid":30478,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"DUO臨開show先病, 場場打針開聲, 搞到把聲過左兩年都仲係拆拆地<br />\n